o></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4013320/extras/85a75be0d4e4b7c54d0ea6af2c27a356.avif?t=1760979572\" width=502 height=246 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔥 <strong>Build your own harem</strong> — gather loyalty, beauty, and talent to forge a power base like no other.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >👑 <strong>Intrigue &amp; betrayal</strong> — outsmart the scheming priest and prove yourself worthy of the throne.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💋 <strong>Five sensual heroines</strong> — each heroine has her own story, secrets, and unique desires waiting to be discovered.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🏰 <strong>Dark legacy</strong> — restore a ruined province and turn it into a thriving domain under your rule.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎭 <strong>Choices that matter</strong> — your decisions shape not only your rise to power, but also your pleasures.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4013320/extras/7f38ecb965a660c58563be019f92d912.poster.avif?t=1760979572\" width=600 height=368 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4013320/extras/7f38ecb965a660c58563be019f92d912.webm?t=1760979572\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4013320/extras/7f38ecb965a660c58563be019f92d912.mp4?t=1760979572\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>", "short_description": "Framed at your coronation and exiled to a fallen province, you must rebuild power, uncover desire, and forge a harem of loyalty and passion. Outsmart betrayal, seduce allies, and prove you can rule with both strength and pleasure.", 